{"id": 243322006, "title": "Jay Slater: Volunteers to begin huge Tenerife search", "text": "Mr Slater's mother Debbie Duncan previously told the BBC her son was on his first holiday abroad without parents. \"He's just an all-round nice, bubbly guy with hundreds of friends who love being in his company,\" she said. \"He's gorgeous, he's beautiful. He's my baby.\" Mr Hargreaves' mother Rachel Hargreaves said she and her son were staying in Tenerife with Ms Duncan for \"as long as it takes\". She said: \"You can\u2019t put into words how you feel. I\u2019m just here trying to support and be strong for her. \"The things she can\u2019t do I am trying to do for her, mother-to-mother.\"", "summary": "Spanish police called on volunteers with expertise of harsh terrain to help find the 19-year-old.", "url": "https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c147lldzwvro", "image": "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/branded_news/54c7/live/54973dc0-356d-11ef-8a9e-3d3777b54bad.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-29 04:52:19", "author": "Jonny Humphries", "authors": ["Jonny Humphries"], "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "gb", "sentiment": 0.336}